There is a folder for each operating system. Each folder contain a Dockerfile and a conf.yml file.



Example for conf.yml

app_search:
  file_name: 
    Makefile
    Makefile.target
  cmd: make

new_url: https://github.com/contiki-ng/contiki-ng.git



conf.yml file has 
-file_name: the name of files to be search for to identify the applications directory. 
-cmd: the build command which will be excuted in the application directory.
-new_url: the url to the new version of the operating system.

